      "date": "2013-11-27 08:22:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified; Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\nHere is the test result of recovery-double-scale with FSTYPE=zfs and FAILURE_MODE=HARD:\n https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b8823628-572f-11e3-8d5c-52540035b04c\n\nBefore the test was stopped due to client-15 unreachable issue, the following sub-tests passed:\n test 1: failover MDS, then OST\n test 2: failover MDS, then 2 clients\n test 3: skipped due to less than 2 MDTs\n test 4: failover OST, then another OST\n\nThe original failure reported in LU-3286 was fixed.\n\nLai, could you please back-port the patch to Lustre b2_4 branch? Thanks!",
